TSHIMOLOLO

'''Tobane'''  ke motsana oo mo botlhaba jwa lefatshe la [[Botswana|Botswana ]]go tsamaya sekgele se se masome a mabedi go tsweng mo toropong ee epang kopore/nikile ya [[Selebi-Phikwe|Selebi-Phikwe]].. Seemo sa bosa ke boemo jwa 21° 57' 0" borwa, 27° 54' 0" botlhaba<ref>http://www.maplandia.com/botswana/central-region/selebi-phikwe/tobane/</ref>.

DITSO TSA MOTSE

Monni wa motsana  ebong kgosana ya motsana Rre Godfrey Manowe o tlhalosa gore Tobane ke motse wa Batlokwa oo simolotsweng ke batho ba ba tlileng e le batshabi go tswa Aferika Borwa ka dintlwa tsa mefare tsa nako ya bo 1800s.Banni ba Tobane ba simolotse go nna kwa Shoshong pele le Bangwato gape ba ya go nna kwa Serorome(ebong Palapye gompieno) pele fa ba ya kwa Makome go bapa le Mmadinare ka ngwaga wa 1901.Morago ga nako segopa se se ne sa sutlisiwa gape ,mme ba ikaega  kwa bophirima jwa Noka ya Tobane.Mme ba tlolela ka kwa ntheng e nngwe ya noka e bong Tobane gompieno.

DITIRELO

Motsana o o nale tsela ee tswelang kwa toropong e. Go nale noka ee tona ee ralalang motsana ee bidiwang Motloutse ka kwa bokone-botlhaba.Motsana o o nale ditlamelo tse dintsi jaaka metsi aa phepa go tswa letlamong la Shashe, motlakase,kgokelelo ya megala ya letlheka ka ba kompone ya Mascom le Orange. E nale gape ditirelo tsa megala ka ba kompone ya Botswana ee dirang le megala. Go nale kokelwana, sekolo se se botlana, le se sogolwane mo tikologong. Palo ya batho ke kgobololo ya selekanyo sa makgolokgolo,makgolo a robabongwe,masome a mabedi le botlhano <ref>http://population.mongabay.com/population/botswana/933002/tobane</ref>

BOKHUTLO

Le fa motsana wa Tobane o sa itsege thata mo Botswana,dipalo tsa batho tsone di a golo ka moo se se ka rotloetsa dithabolo tse di tseneletseng.Motsana o tla thabologa mo dingwageng tse di latelang ntateng ya toropo ya Selibe Phikwe ee epang ditswa mmung.




